{
  "texts": [
    "However, as students become more comfortable with AI tools, their interaction with such tools might increases, suggesting that getting familiar with AI and having training about prompting skills can enhance the integration of AI into learning processes.",
    "It might imply the need for targeted interventions to support students in becoming adept users of AI, maximizing its potential to enhance their learning experiences.",
    "This study also has several limitations.",
    "First, since it was conducted in a natural classroom environment, students might have used other resources without reporting them.",
    "Second, prompt analysis was based on the ChatGPT conversation history that students voluntarily uploaded, which may not capture all interactions; using an LMS-embedded LLM tool could have provided a more comprehensive record."
  ]
}